{"tid":1185832,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"近排759有隻朱古力勁好食","createTime":"2019-06-04T13:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T18:23:20.000Z","uid":119393,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"65c95bf502c3cc91a51cccc53f710592599a5f0c","tid":1185832,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:38:08.000Z","msg":"已經第五包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M3Y43dL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM3Y43dL.jpg&h=dc56d4a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一包有三隻味<br />\n1. 苦朱古力+曲奇+朱古力醬<br />\n2. 焦糖醬+吉士朱古力<br />\n3.苦朱古力+吉士朱古力+棉花糖<br />\n三隻都好味<br />\n<br />\n呢個牌子香港好少入<br />\n入極都係綠茶/黃豆粉味<br />\n就算去日資百貨都係多隻普通雜錦味<br />\n今次估計759都只會入一水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a63b8d7f435e32c1405e17c186ddf3d6bef8ae6","tid":1185832,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"苦朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46eb8b37e26fa3771bab175257a6d73b746d6532","tid":1185832,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a63b8d7f435e32c1405e17c186ddf3d6bef8ae6","tid":1185832,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"苦朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:45:37.000Z","msg":"佢成份真係寫bitter chocolate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd0b66e7b4688ba11fc2ed59cfac6b5b39a1da3","tid":1185832,"uid":113061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T14:21:39.000Z